---
description: React frontend — API client and i18n
globs:
  - "frontend/src/**/*.js"
  - "frontend/src/**/*.css"
alwaysApply: false
---

Source of truth:

- `frontend/TRANSLATIONS.md` — all UI strings in `LanguageContext.js` (`T.pl` / `T.en`)
- `frontend/src/api.js` — HTTP client; changes require `docs/backend-migration/API_CONTRACT.md` update

During FastAPI migration: **avoid frontend edits** unless fixing a confirmed bug or explicitly adding features.

API base URL: `REACT_APP_API_URL` or `http://localhost:5001`.
